OL,3,C'All communities' want to see grooming
OL,4,Cgangs punished, says Council leader
OL,6,FA Council Leader has said that all
OL,7,Fcommunities want nothing more than to
OL,8,Fsee the members of grooming gangs
OL,9,F"punished to the full extent of the
OL,10,Flaw."
OL,12,FOldham Council Leader Arooj Shah
OL,13,Fwelcomed a national report from
OL,14,FBaroness Louise Casey, which looked at
OL,15,Fthe scale of grooming gangs across the
OL,16,Fcountry and the failure to recognise
OL,17,Fhow ethnicity affected local
OL,18,Finvestigations.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
