OL,3,C'All communities' want to see grooming
OL,4,Cgangs punished, says Council leader
OL,6,FCllr Shah said: "So clearly on the
OL,7,Fback of Baroness Casey's report, she
OL,8,Fmade it very explicit and clear that
OL,9,Fthere was, she felt her findings found
OL,10,Fthat there was some reluctancy to
OL,11,Fdiscuss ethnicity.
OL,13,F"Child Sexual abuse is perpetrated by
OL,14,Fpeople of all races and religions, and
OL,15,Finflicted on people of all races and
OL,16,Freligions. But that doesn't mean we
OL,17,Fshouldn't ask questions about any
OL,18,Fdrivers of this very specific type of
OL,19,Foffending.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
