OL,3,C'All communities' want to see grooming
OL,4,Cgangs punished, says Council leader
OL,6,F"We need to do more to understand why
OL,7,Fthis particular pattern of abuse is
OL,8,Fmore prevalent among some groups of
OL,9,Fmen.
OL,11,F"To say so is not racist. What is
OL,12,Fracist is to suggest that all
OL,13,FPakistani men are groomers or the
OL,14,Fimplication, the suggestion, that any
OL,15,Fone community condones this behaviour
OL,16,F- it does not.
OL,18,F"Nobody I have spoken to, from any
OL,19,Fcommunity, wants to see anything other
OL,20,Fthan for these men to be punished to
OL,21,Fthe full extent of the law."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
