OL,3,C'All communities' want to see grooming
OL,4,Cgangs punished, says Council leader
OL,6,FThe report criticised local
OL,7,Fauthorities for failing to understand
OL,8,Fthe nature and scale of young girls
OL,9,Fbeing exploited.
OL,11,FOldham has been the subject of a
OL,12,Fnumber of investigations into grooming
OL,13,Fgangs and sexual exploitation dating
OL,14,Fas far back as 2006.
OL,16,FResponding to the report, Cllr Arooj
OL,17,FShah said: "In Oldham, we recognise
OL,18,Fthe failings of the past and are
OL,19,Fdetermined not to repeat them.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
