OL,3,C'All communities' want to see grooming
OL,4,Cgangs punished, says Council leader
OL,6,FA local review published in 2022 found
OL,7,Fthat Greater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,8,Fand Oldham Council had failed a number
OL,9,Fof young girls who became the victims
OL,10,Fof grooming and child sexual
OL,11,Fexploitation. At the time, both
OL,12,Forganisations said they were "deeply
OL,13,Fsorry" to all those affected.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
