OL,3,C'All communities' want to see grooming
OL,4,Cgangs punished, says Council leader
OL,6,FBaroness Casey's National Audit found
OL,7,Fthat the ethnicity of those involved
OL,8,Fin grooming gangs has been "shied away
OL,9,Ffrom" by authorities, and there was
OL,10,Fenough evidence in Greater Manchester
OL,11,Fthat there was "disproportionate
OL,12,Fnumbers of men from Asian ethnic
OL,13,Fbackgrounds amongst suspects for group-
OL,14,Fbased child sexual exploitation".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
