OL,3,C'All communities' want to see grooming
OL,4,Cgangs punished, says Council leader
OL,6,FWhile Cllr Shah said investigations
OL,7,Fshould not shy away from asking why
OL,8,Fpatterns abuse are more prevalent in
OL,9,Fcertain groups, she highlighted that
OL,10,Fit is not Oldham's South Asian
OL,11,Fcommunity that needs to ask these
OL,12,Fquestions but instead the authorities.
OL,14,FShe said: "I don't think there's
OL,15,Fanything about reflection or inward
OL,16,Flooking because that makes the
OL,17,Fassumption that there's been denial
OL,18,Ffrom a community about this.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
