OL,3,C'All communities' want to see grooming
OL,4,Cgangs punished, says Council leader
OL,6,F"As far as the community's concerned,
OL,7,Fthe Pakistani community, the South
OL,8,FAsian community, is like any other
OL,9,Fcommunity, a crime is a crime."
OL,11,FOldham Council became the subject of
OL,12,Finternational headlines in January,
OL,13,Fafter the Labour Government denied
OL,14,Ftheir request for a public inquiry.
OL,16,FThe refusal was criticised by Tech
OL,17,Fbillionaire Elon Musk, sparking a wave
OL,18,Fof interest in grooming gangs in
OL,19,FOldham, which eventually gave way to
OL,20,Fcalls for a UK-wide child sex abuse
OL,21,Finquiry.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
