OL,3,C'All communities' want to see grooming
OL,4,Cgangs punished, says Council leader
OL,6,FThe Prime Minister Sir Keir Starmer
OL,7,Finitially denied this request, and
OL,8,Finstead set up a number of local
OL,9,Finvestigations into individual towns
OL,10,Facross the country.
OL,12,FHowever the latest review from
OL,13,FBaroness Casey laid out a number of
OL,14,Frecommendations for the Government,
OL,15,Fone of which was to hold a full
OL,16,Fnational inquiry that co-ordinates
OL,17,Ftargeted local investigations into
OL,18,Fabuse.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
