OL,3,C'All communities' want to see grooming
OL,4,Cgangs punished, says Council leader
OL,6,FThe Government has now accepted all of
OL,7,Fthe recommendations including the
OL,8,Finquiry; something which Oldham
OL,9,FCouncil has welcomed.
OL,11,FCllr Shah said: "We share Baroness
OL,12,FCasey's desire to see a national
OL,13,Finquiry, which is why we requested one
OL,14,Fto be commissioned back in February.
OL,16,F"reI hope that this report will make
OL,17,Fit clear that this must happen, for
OL,18,Fthe sake of everyone affected by child
OL,19,Fsexual exploitation, and that
OL,20,Fsurvivors' voices will be at the heart
OL,21,Fof it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
