OL,3,C'All communities' want to see grooming
OL,4,Cgangs punished, says Council leader
OL,6,F"We are working with the Home Office
OL,7,Fto understand how the local and
OL,8,Fnational inquiries will align, and we
OL,9,Fare in conversation to get clarity and
OL,10,Fnext steps."
OL,12,FCllr Shah also welcomed calls from a
OL,13,Fnumber of victims and activists,
OL,14,Fincluding former Greater Manchester
OL,15,FPolice detective Maggie Oliver, to see
OL,16,Fthose who failed in their duties to
OL,17,Fsafeguard victims face the justice
OL,18,Fsystem.
